data.description: NEW ROOF in 2022.  NO HOA Dues!  Step through beautiful front doors into this South Florida style home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  Just off the foyer is a dining area that could double as office space, music room, or additional living room.  The great room has a corner fireplace for cozy nights and another beautiful set of doors leading to the covered patio and privacy fenced back yard.  Updated kitchen includes walk in pantry, matching stainless appliances, glass tile back splash, granite countertops.  The main bedroom is roomy with tray ceiling and ensuite bath.  Main bath has two walk in closets and double vanity.  Split floor plan gives privacy to the main bedroom.  The Ring Home alarm system allows for coded keyless entry and remote monitoring.  New gas water heater approximately 3 years ago.  All appliances including washer and dryer, all televisions, and Ring system convey.  Some furniture is available for negotiation.  This home is located minutes from the back gate of Pensacola NAS, the Navy hospital/exchange, beaches at Perdido Key and Orange Beach, Big Lagoon State Park, National Seashore Park at Johnson Beach, Tarkiln Bayou Preserve State Park, Blue Angel Recreation/RV Park, and more conveniences.  Buyer to verify room dimensions, lot size, and GLA.
